      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Doujutsu)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 4 (Spell Level 2)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 21</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You disrupt the rhythm of the target's heartbeat. If the subject has fewer than 6 HD, it dies. Otherwise, the subject takes 4d6 damage, which cannot reduce them below 0 HP.</p>\n\n\n\n",
